headline: 3 Reasons to Avoid WST and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: West Pharmaceutical Services has followed the market’s trajectory closely, rising in tandem with the S&P 500 over the past six months. The stock has climbed by 16.3% to $260.31 per share while the index has gained 18.6%.
